PN,31801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780689960
OL,3,CZelenskyy asks for face-to-face
OL,4,Cmeeting with Putin in public message
OL,6,FUkrainian President Volodymyr
OL,7,FZelenskyy has called for a face-to-
OL,8,Fface meeting with Vladimir Putin in a
OL,9,Fpublic letter addressed directly to
OL,10,Fthe Russian president.
OL,12,FThe letter, posted on social media on
OL,13,FThursday, was the first public message
OL,14,FZelenskyy has written directly to
OL,15,FPutin since Russia launched its full-
OL,16,Fscale invasion of Ukraine in 2022, and
OL,17,Famounted to a sweeping of the Russian
OL,18,Fleader's 26 years in power.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780689960
OL,3,CZelenskyy asks for face-to-face
OL,4,Cmeeting with Putin in public message
OL,6,FZelenskyy acknowledged shifting US
OL,7,Fpriorities, saying it would be wrong
OL,8,Fto simply wait for the Trump
OL,9,Fadministration to turn its focus back
OL,10,Fto ending the war in Ukraine while it
OL,11,Fremains heavily focused on the war
OL,12,Fwith Iran.
OL,14,F"When you came to power in Russia more
OL,15,Fthan 26 years ago, many people in
OL,16,FUkraine viewed you positively. That is
OL,17,Fhow it was. But that is now in the
OL,18,Fpast," Zelenskyy wrote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780689960
OL,3,CZelenskyy asks for face-to-face
OL,4,Cmeeting with Putin in public message
OL,6,F"Now, the overwhelming majority of
OL,7,FUkrainians view it positively that our
OL,8,Flong-range drones paid a visit to the
OL,9,Fopening of your forum in St.
OL,10,FPetersburg, covering a distance of
OL,11,Fmore than 1,000 kilometres.
OL,13,F"As you know very well, that distance
OL,14,Fis not the limit of our capabilities."
OL,16,FHe added: "I am proposing a meeting."
OL,18,FUS President Donald Trump said it
OL,19,F"would be great" if Putin and
OL,20,FZelenskyy met. "They should get it
OL,21,Fdone," Trump said.
OL,26,@xD@KOU{D@AOU{D@PO]|D@POU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780689960
OL,3,CZelenskyy asks for face-to-face
OL,4,Cmeeting with Putin in public message
OL,6,FAsked what concessions he had urged
OL,7,FPutin to make to end the war, Trump
OL,8,Fdeclined to provide details but said
OL,9,Fboth sides would need to compromise.
OL,11,F"They're going to both make
OL,12,Fcompromises," he said. "I suggested
OL,13,Fthose compromises."
OL,15,FZelenskyy appeared to be trying to
OL,16,Fseize a pivotal moment in the war, as
OL,17,FUkraine has regained some leverage on
OL,18,Fthe battlefield through improved long-
OL,19,Frange strike capabilities that have
OL,20,Fcomplicated Russia's advances.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@MO]tD@XOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780689960
OL,3,CZelenskyy asks for face-to-face
OL,4,Cmeeting with Putin in public message
OL,6,FAt the same time, Moscow has stepped
OL,7,Fup its aerial attacks across Ukraine,
OL,8,Fseeking to exploit Kyiv's shortages
OL,9,Fand continued vulnerability to
OL,10,Fballistic missile strikes.
OL,12,FHe said any talks should be held in a
OL,13,Fneutral third country, ruling out both
OL,14,FMoscow and Kyiv as venues.
OL,16,FHe suggested Switzerland, Turkey or
OL,17,FArab states as possible hosts for
OL,18,Fnegotiations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780689960
OL,3,CZelenskyy asks for face-to-face
OL,4,Cmeeting with Putin in public message
OL,6,F"It is leaders who resolve the key
OL,7,Fissues. That has always been the case,
OL,8,Fand it always will be," he wrote. "I
OL,9,Fpropose to set a clear date for such a
OL,10,Fmeeting."
OL,12,FHe added that Ukrainian intelligence
OL,13,Fsuggested Russia was considering plans
OL,14,Fto extend the war into 2027 and 2028,
OL,15,Fwhile increasingly relying on
OL,16,Fballistic missile strikes to gain
OL,17,Fground, something that its ground
OL,18,Fcampaign has failed to accomplish.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@WO]pD@cOUrD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780689960
OL,3,CZelenskyy asks for face-to-face
OL,4,Cmeeting with Putin in public message
OL,6,FZelenskyy also accused Moscow of
OL,7,Ftrying to draw Belarus deeper into the
OL,8,Fwar and of seeking to destabilise
OL,9,FTransnistria, the Russia-backed
OL,10,Fbreakaway region of Moldova.
OL,12,FThe Ukrainian president said Russia
OL,13,Fwas increasingly feeling the cost of
OL,14,Fthe conflict, citing drone strikes
OL,15,Fdeep inside Russian territory,
OL,16,Feconomic pressure, fuel shortages,
OL,17,Frising prices and the need for further
OL,18,Fmilitary mobilisation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780689960
OL,3,CZelenskyy asks for face-to-face
OL,4,Cmeeting with Putin in public message
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHe claimed Russia suffered more than
OL,12,F30,000 soldiers killed or seriously
OL,13,Fwounded in May alone, saying Ukraine
OL,14,Fhad video evidence of the losses and
OL,15,Fthat similar casualty levels had been
OL,16,Fsustained for months.
OL,18,FZelenskyy acknowledged that Ukraine
OL,19,Fcontinued to suffer significant losses
OL,20,Fdespite what he described as a more
OL,21,Ffavourable casualty ratio.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780689960
OL,3,CZelenskyy asks for face-to-face
OL,4,Cmeeting with Putin in public message
OL,6,FHe said Ukraine was prepared to
OL,7,Fimplement a full ceasefire for the
OL,8,Fduration of any negotiations.
OL,10,FHe proposed an all-for-all prisoner
OL,11,Fexchange as a first step towards
OL,12,Fending the war. He also called for the
OL,13,Freturn of civilians and children taken
OL,14,Ffrom Ukraine during the conflict.
OL,16,F"The world has not grown tired of
OL,17,FUkraine, as you long hoped it would.
OL,18,FBut there is growing fatigue with
OL,19,FRussia," Zelenskyy said.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@HO]
